                 ;________________________________________
                 ;
                 ;    Main loop
                 ;
8B9F  AD 01 DC   L01045  LDA $DC01           ; JOYSTICK PORT B
8BA2  C9 DF              CMP #$DF            ; Is CBM key pressed?
8BA4  D0 1B              BNE L01048
8BA6  A9 01              LDA #$01            ; CBM key is pressed, so pause game
8BA8  8D CB 02           STA $02CB           ; Game paused boolean
8BAB  AD 01 DC   L01046  LDA $DC01           ; JOYSTICK PORT B
8BAE  C9 7F              CMP #$7F            ; Is RUN/STOP pressed?
8BB0  D0 03              BNE L01047
8BB2  4C 15 80           JMP L00921          ; RUN/STOP is pressed, so quit game
8BB5  AD 00 DC   L01047  LDA $DC00           ; JOYSTICK PORT A
8BB8  29 10              AND #$10            ; Is FIRE pressed?
8BBA  D0 EF              BNE L01046
8BBC  A9 00              LDA #$00            ; FIRE is pressed, so un-pause game
8BBE  8D CB 02           STA $02CB           ; Game paused boolean
8BC1  20 66 89   L01048  JSR L01014

                 ;________________________________________
                 ;
                 ;    Object definitions
                 ;
                 ;    The 4th, 8th, ... , byte specifies:
                 ;
                 ;    BIT   Meaning
                 ;    7     Expand in X-dir
                 ;    6     Expand in Y-dir
                 ;    5     Unused
                 ;    4     Multicolor
                 ;    3-0   Color
                 ;
9F84  00                 BYTE $00            ; SPRITE PTR to Swinging rope
9F85  04                 BYTE $04            ; X displacement for Swinging rope sprite
9F86  00                 BYTE $00            ; Y displacement for Swinging rope sprite         
9F87  5F                 BYTE $5F            ; No X-Expand, Y-Expand, Multicolor, Color=#$0F
9F88  01                 BYTE $01            ; SPRITE PTR to Swinging rope
9F89  04                 BYTE $04            ; X displacement for Swinging rope sprite
9F8A  2A                 BYTE $2A            ; Y displacement for Swinging rope sprite
